Package org.eclipse.e4.ui.model.application.ui Description

Application programming interfaces describing the Eclipse 4 state and container model elements.

Package Specification

The package provides interfaces that describe the Eclipse 4 state and container model. These elements include descriptions of containers, factories, objects and state elements.
